uot%3B%20Palmer%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20give%20people%20a%20chance%20to%20ask%20their%20three%20or%20four%20questions%20right%20up%20front%2C%20then%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20read%20through%2025%20pages%20on%20my%20website%20to%20find%20the%20policy%20position%20they%20care%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'It%20is%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20position%20and%20get%20it%20sometimes%20better'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20took%20less%20than%20%2425%2C000%20for%20his%20campaign%20to%20build%20version%20one%20of%20PalmerAI%2C%20adding%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20impressed%26quot%3B%20with%20how%20it%20turned%20out.%20The%20bot%20came%20to%20life%20after%20Palmer%20spent%20several%20hours%20recording%20himself%20reading%20speeches%20and%20excerpts%20from%20books%20to%20capture%20his%20voice%2C%20and%20his%20campaign%20plans%20to%20improve%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vows-to-make-xai-chatbot-grok-politically-neutral-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebot's%20responses%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20continue%20operations%20across%20the%2016%20states%20and%20territories%20where%20Palmer%20is%20listed%20on%20the%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20its%20residents%20aren't%20able%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20general%20election%2C%20American%20Samoa%20has%20turned%20out%20unexpected%20primary%20results%20before.%20In%202020%2C%20billionaire%20Michael%20Bloomberg's%20only%20win%20in%20the%20Democratic%20primaries%20came%20from%20the%20territory.%20Despite%20the%20odds%2C%20Palmer%20hopes%20his%20win%20there%20will%20create%20momentum%20for%20his%20campaign%20in%20states%20like%20Arizona%2C%20Kansas%2C%20and%20Missouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20position%20and%20get%20it%20sometimes%20better%20than%20even%20if%20you%20ask%20me%20the%20question.%20If%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20I'm%20too%20verbose%20and%20I%