20yet%20to%20be%20replaced.%20While%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20depleted%20leadership%20is%20bound%20to%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20also%20critical%20as%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20and%20Election%20Commission%20itself%20face%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opaque%2C%20anonymous%20system%20of%20election%20financing%20that%20the%20top%20court%20last%20month%20struck%20down%20as%20unconstitutional%20will%20come%20up%20again%C2%A0%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20when%20a%20five-judge%20bench%20will%20hear%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20plea%20that%20it%20will%20only%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20reveal%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20donors%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20others%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%20The%20SBI%20had%20been%20ordered%20to%20make%20all%20details%20public%20by%20March%206%20and%20the%20court%20is%20also%20due%20to%20take%20up%20a%20contempt%20petition%20against%20the%20government-owned%20bank%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Election%20Commission%20which%20now%20just%20has%20one%20election%20commissioner%20gives%20an%20impression%20of%20governance%20in%20disarray.%20The%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20appoint%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20replacement%20nearly%20a%20month%20after%20his%20slot%20became%20vacant%20and%20has%20not%20even%20convened%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20three-remember%20selection%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20overseeing%20and%20ensuring%20free%20and%20fair%20voting%20in%20all%20543%20parliamentary%20constituencies%2C%20the%20three%20election%20commissioners%20are%20also%20tasked%20with%20making%20sure%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20leaders%20stick%20to%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20election%20law%2C%20especially%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20which%20prohibits%20the%20misuse%20of%20government%20machinery%20by%20ruling%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20use%20of%20appeals%20to%20religion%20and%20hate%20speech%20as%20a%20means%20of%20gathering%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20%E2%80%93%20both%20its%20unexplained%20nature%20and%20the%20timing%20%E2%80%93%20will%20raise%20concerns%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20key%20electoral%20institution%20and%20the%20processes%20in%20place%20for%20its%20autonomous%20functioning.%20It%20is%20upon%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20independence%20that%20claims%20of%20%E2%80%98free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20rests%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20controversial%20appointment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20exit%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20so%20did%20the%20manner%20and%20speed%20with%20which%20he%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20crucial%20job%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2017%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20began%20hearing%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20appoint%20election%20commissioners%20of%20its%20own%20choice%20and%20arguing%20that%20this%20process%20violated%20the%20constitutional%20requirement%20that%20the%20ECI%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20executive.%20Even%20as%20the%20apex%20court%20was%20seized%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-pil-seeking-quashing-of-appointment-of-arun-goel-as-election-commissioner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Modi%20government%20rushed%20through%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20serving%20bureaucrat%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20on%20November%2018%2C%202022%2C%20and%20was%20appointed%20as%20election%20commissioner%20the%20very%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-pil-challenging-appointment-of-election-commissioner-arun-goel-101691130602648.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeventually%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20challenging%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20made%20scathing%20comments%20on%20his%20hurried%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20procedures%20commencing%20with%20the%20proposal%2C%20processing%20of%20the%20same%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Minister%20for%20Law%2C%20the%20further%20recommendations%20of%20the%20concerned%20officers%2C%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20acceptance%20of%20the%20application%20of%20the%20appointee%20seeking%20voluntary%20retirement%2C%20waiving%20the%20three%20months%20period%20and%20the%20appointment%20by%20the%20President%20under%20Article%20324(2)%2C%20which%20came%20to%20be%20notified%2C%20took%20place%20in%20a%20single%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2Fqjxoo%23selection-1449.0-1456.0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20court%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%202023%2C%20a%20constitution%20bench%20said%20that%20all%20those%20appointed%20as%20election%20commissioners%2C%20including%20the%20CEC%20and%20his%2Fher%20two%20colleagues%2C%20should%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20president%20of%20India%20only%20on%20the%20advice%20by%20a%20committee%20comprising%20prime%20minister%2C%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20opposition%20and%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Modi%20government%20disregarded%20this%20judgment%20and%20instead%20passed%20a%20law%20which%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20comprising%20the%20PM%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20a%20third%20member%2C%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20Union%20Cabinet%20Minister%20to%20be%20nominated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20thereby%20giving%20the%20executive%20the%20same%20power%20of%20appointment%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20sought%20to%20curtail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%20resignation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoel%E2%80%99s%20is%20the%20second%20unusual%20departure%20of%20an%20election%20commissioner%20in%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20and%20both%20of%20these%20exits%20have%20happened%20during%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202020%2C%20Ashok%20Lavasa%2C%20then%20an%20EC%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpresident-kovind-accepts-ashok-lavasas-resignation-from-post-of-election-commissioner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%C2%A0%20joined%20the%20ADB%20in%20Manilla.%20He%20was%20slated%20to%20go%20on%20to%20become%20CEC%20as%20per%20the%20seniority%20principle%20among%20the%20ECs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20he%20was%20the%20only%20election%20commissioner%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fcover-story%2Farticle29618205.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAshok%252520Lavasa%252520was%252520the%252520sole%2Cthe%252520price%252520for%252520his%252520dissent.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20give%20a%20clean%20chit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20electoral%20process%20violations%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20A%20few%20months%20after%20the%20election%2C%20his%20wife%20was%20served%20with%2