gcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECHAIDEER%20MAHYUDDIN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pilot%20and%20copilot%20of%20a%20domestic%20flight%20in%20Indonesia%20fell%20asleep%20for%2028%20minutes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20pilots%20said%20he%20suffered%20from%20poor%20sleep%20the%20day%20before%20the%20flight%2C%20a%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20plane%2C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Ecarrying%20153%20people%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20landed%20safely%20in%20the%20Indonesian%20capital%20of%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20and%20copilot%20of%20a%20domestic%20flight%20in%20Indonesia%20carrying%20153%20people%20fell%20asleep%20for%20nearly%2030%20minutes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fknkt.go.id%2FRepo%2FFiles%2FLaporan%2FPenerbangan%2F2024%2FKNKT.24.01.02.04-Preliminary-Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20published%20by%20Indonesia's%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Committee%20(KNKT)%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20in%20January%20on%20a%20return%20flight%20from%20Kendari%2C%20in%20the%20Indonesian%20province%20of%20Southeast%20Sulawesi%2C%20to%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20of%20the%20Batik%20Air%20%3Cspan%3EAirbus%20%3C%2Fspan%3EA320%20aircraft%2C%2032%2C%20took%20a%20nap%20after%20getting%20permission%20from%20his%20copilot%20while%20the%20plane%20was%20at%20a%20cruising%20altitude%20of%2036%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2045%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20captain%20woke%20up%20and%20offered%20to%20let%20the%20copilot%2C%2028%2C%20rest%2C%20but%20they%20declined%2C%20and%20the%20captain%20fell%20back%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20officer%20spent%20roughly%20the%20next%2020%20minutes%20communicating%20with%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20and%20flight%20attendants%20before%20they%20%26quot%3Binadvertently%26quot%3B%20also%20fell%20asleep%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20minutes%20after%20the%20copilot's%20last%20recorded%20transmission%2C%20the%20captain%20woke%20up%20and%20saw%20that%20his%20second%20in%20command%20was%20asleep%20and%20that%20they%20had%20flown%20off-course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20waking%20them%2C%20the%20captain%20answered%20another%20pilot's%20call%20and%20air%20traffic%20controllers%2C%20claiming%20they%20had%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bradio%20communication%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20later%20landed%20in%20Jakarta%20without%20any%20further%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20long-haul%20flights%20have%20relief%20pilots%20to%20ensure%20each%20pilot%20is%20sufficiently%20rested%20when%20they%20take%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20short-haul%20flights%20such%20as%20the%20Batik%20Air%20flight%2C%20which%20takes%20roughly%20two%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflightsafety.org%2Fasw-article%2Fcontrolled-rest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtrolled%20rest%20periods%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20common%3A%20One%20pilot%20can%20briefly%20catch%20some%20shut-eye%20while%20the%20other%20continues%20monitoring%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20manage%20fatigue%20and%20improve%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20KNKT%20report%2C%20the%20second%20in%20command%20had%20not%20rested%20sufficiently%20the%20night%20before%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20pilots'%20identities%20but%20said%20both%20were%20Indonesian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20acknowledged%20%26quot%3Bthe%20safety%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20aircraft%20operator%20and%20considered%20that%20the%20safety%20actions%20were%20relevant%20to%20improve%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20did%20make%20some%20safety%20recommendations%20over%20adding%20guidance%20on%20checking%20pilots'%20physical%20and%20mental%20conditions%20and%20carrying%20out%20cockpit%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatik%20Air%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Boperates%20with%20adequate%20rest%20policy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20implement%20all%20safety%20recommendation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-13176837%2FPilot-pilot-fall-ASLEEP-28-minutes-passenger-flight-Indonesia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMailOnline%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Batik%20Air%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710009431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eca6dfce7f1785b2e8430e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20occurred%20on%20a%20Batik%20Air%20return%20flight%20carrying%20153%20people%20to%20the%20Indonesian%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmanley%40businessinsider.com%20(Cameron%20Manley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dating%20apps%20confused%20by%20military%20GPS%20jamming%20could%20explain%20why%20Lebanon's%20citizens%20are%20suddenly%20being%20matched%20with%20Israelis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20taken%20from%20northern%20Israel%2C%20along%20the%20border%20with%20southern%20Lebanon%20on%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20shows%20smoke%20billowing%20following%20Israeli%20bombardment%20on%20the%20Lebanese%20village%20of%20Markaba.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%2