0post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20said%20the%20mindset%20to%20add%20new%20dimensions%20to%20his%20bowling%20has%20worked%20well%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20can%20try%20something%2C%20I%20don't%20hold%20back.%20I%20have%20kept%20my%20ears%20and%20eyes%20open%20to%20listen%20to%20good%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20I%20try%2C%20I%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20learn.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20sticking%20to%20one%20method%20won't%20work.%20But%20thankfully%20experimenting%20and%20learning%20has%20helped%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20marked%20his%20spell%20on%20Saturday%20(5%2F77)%20and%20the%20one%20in%20England's%20second%20innings%20at%20Ranchi%20(5%2F51)%20as%20his%20best%20outings%20in%20the%20five-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20happy%20with%20the%20way%20the%20ball%20came%20out%20(in%20those%20spells)%2C%20as%20most%20pleased%20with%20this%20performance%20and%20the%20second%20innings%20in%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%20sometimes%20the%20beauty%20is%20what's%20gone%20by.%20What%20went%20by%20was%20on%20his%20head%20(the%20way%20he%20set%20up%20Ollie%20Pope%20in%20Ranchi).%20I%20was%20expecting%20him%20to%20reverse%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20lavished%20praise%20on%20left-arm%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20who%20ended%20up%20with%2019%20wickets%20from%20four%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20ball%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20Kuldeep's%20hands%20is%20unbelievable.%20Watching%20a%20wrist%20spinner%20in%20such%20a%20flow%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20switches%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20make%20through%20the%20series%20and%20over%20the%20last%2010%20months%20is%20so%20heartening%20to%20see.%20I%20can't%20be%20happier%20for%20somebody%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ashwin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E