20variant%2C%20too%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Ci%3EWande%20tchali%2C%20sheen%20gali%2C%20beyi%20yee%20bahaar%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20Peerzada%20Ghulam%20Ahmad%20%E2%80%98Mehjoor%E2%80%99%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20national%20poet%20for%20some%2C%20which%20loosely%20translates%20to%3A%20%E2%80%98Spring%E2%80%99s%20advent%20shall%20kick%20out%20the%20winter%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20a%20million%20tapestries%20of%20greens%20and%20greys%20and%20crimsons%20and%20turquoises%20should%20embrace%20the%20girdle%20of%20alps%20and%20mountains%20cradling%20the%20many%20valleys%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08175551%2Fdownload.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22243%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700822%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22365%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKashmir%20%E2%80%93%20Travels%20in%20Paradise%20on%20Earth%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Romesh%20Bhattacharji.%20Publisher%3A%20Harper%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20book%20by%20Romesh%20Bhattacharji%20(%3Cem%3EKashmir%20%E2%80%93%20Travels%20in%20Paradise%20on%20Earth%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Harper%20Collins)%20has%20shined%20a%20broad%20and%20bright%20spotlight%20on%20this%20scenic%20and%20unspoilt%20landscape%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20the%20countless%20possibilities%20it%20offers%20for%20nature%20lovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20is%20an%20impressive%20achievement%20because%20it%20is%20perhaps%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20comprehensive%20guide%20on%20the%20easy%2C%20moderate%20and%20difficult%20mountain%20traverses%20along%20the%20complete%20portion%20of%20the%20Himalaya%20and%20Pir%20Panjal%20range%20surrounding%20Kashmir.%20Bhattacharji%20confesses%20that%20he%20has%20not%20hit%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20trail%20skirts%20two%20splendid%20alpine%20lakes%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20Sonamarg%20to%20approach%20the%20difficult%20Lakhath%20gali%20(4375m).%20It%20is%20a%20heady%20trail%20which%20was%20taken%20by%20Ernest%20Neve%20and%20Kenneth%20Mason%20to%20make%20the%20first%20ascent%20of%20Mt%20Kolahoi%20(5425m)%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20second%20highest%20peak%2C%20in%201912.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hundred%20and%20ten%20years%20later%2C%20on%20a%20cold%20September%20morning%20in%202022%2C%20Gulzar%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20man%20of%20mountains%20and%20our%20guide%2C%20I%20and%20Riyaz%20Lone%20(of%20Kashmir%20Hikes)%20woke%20up%20near%20the%20steep%2C%20scree-filled%20slopes%20of%20Lakhath%C2%A0%3Ci%3Egali%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0in%20a%20half-pitched%20tent%20strung%20to%20mountain%20boulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20difficult%20night%2C%20we%20were%20truly%20fortunate%20and%20blessed%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20the%20first%20golden%20rays%20of%20sun%20embracing%20the%20northern%20face%20of%20Mt%20Kolahoi%20which%20resembled%20a%20sleeping%20Buddha.%20It%20was%20a%20truly%20jaw-dropping%20moment%20which%20every%20mountain%20lover%20should%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhattacharji%E2%80%99s%20book%20is%20divided%20into%2021%20easy%20chapters%20which%20speak%20admiringly%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccharm%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20nooks%20and%20crannies%2C%20the%20splendour%20of%20its%20lakes%20and%20meadows%2C%20and%20the%20beauty%20of%20its%20valleys%20and%20peaks%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%2018%20chapters%20list%20out%20meticulous%20details%20about%20the%20endless%20trails%20skirting%20up%20and%20down%20a%20range%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfriendly%20mountains%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%20studded%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnecklace%20of%20extravagantly%20beautiful%E2%80%9D%20oligotrophic%20lakes%20and%20tarns.%20As%20the%20author%20points%20out%2C%20some%20of%20these%20nature%E2%80%99s%20wonders%20are%20only%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20hike%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(m