dressing%20the%20underlying%20causes%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20suffering%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20In%20other%20words%20%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20who%20are%20pawns%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hindutva%20forces%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20suffering%20that%20has%20been%20used%20by%20Hindutva%20forces%20for%20their%20own%20purposes.%20The%20two%20are%20very%20different%2C%20is%20that%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENK%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20exactly%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20increased%20polarisation%20%5Band%5D%20communalisation%20makes%20everyone%20insecure%2C%20and%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20help%20it%20and%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20proceeds%20in%20a%20vacuum%20of%20everything%20else%20that%20addressing%20this%20needs%20to%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20by%20the%20way%2C%20just%20to%20respond%20to%20something%20you%20said%20earlier%2C%20because%20%E2%80%A6%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%20I%20need%20to%20emphasise%3B%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20have%20no%20idea%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20read%20what%20the%20ISI%20puts%20out%2C%20I%20have%20no%20whatso%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%A6%20nothing%2C%20no%20love%20lost%20for%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20thing%20that%20ISI%20has%20picked%20up%20on%20it%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20live%20in%20a%20world%20of%20hybrid%20warfare%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20there%E2%80%99s%20some%20%E2%80%A6%20inimical%2C%20anti-India%20forces%20sitting%20somewhere%20clinking%20glasses%20and%20being%20very%20happy%20at%20how%20this%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20woman%2C%20who%E2%80%99s%20actually%20acting%20in%20defence%20of%20Indian%20democratic%20values%2C%20is%20being%20pillaried%20in%20this%20way%20for%20no%20cause.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20no%20control%20over%20how%20people%20selectively%20quo