2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20always%20take%20pain%20explaining%20to%20my%20foreign%20friends%20that%20not%20all%20Indians%20are%20Hindu.%20And%20while%20Indian%20cinema%20is%20famous%20for%20song%20and%20dance%2C%20it%20deserves%20to%20be%20much%20more%20than%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20say%20cinema%20is%20the%20mirror%20of%20society.%20But%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20cinema%20should%20not%20be%20just%20a%20mirror%2C%20but%20a%20prism.%20It%20should%20refract%20societal%20issues%2C%20reveal%20hidden%20facets%2C%20amplify%20injustices%2C%20and%20challenge%20our%20comfort%20with%20narratives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20As%20someone%20who%20spends%20an%20unhealthy%20amount%20of%20time%20watching%20films%2C%20I%20have%20been%20concerned%20about%20Dalit%20depiction%20in%20Indian%20cinema.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDalit%20representation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20mainstream%20celluloid%20is%20scant%2C%20and%20even%20the%20little%20we%20see%20is%20often%20lost%20in%20establishing%20a%20popular%20narrative.%20I%20would%20characterise%20the%20portrayal%20of%20Dalit%20suffering%20as%20Dalit%20porn%20%E2%80%93%20it%20does%20not%20do%20justice%20to%20Dalit%20experiences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEither%20it%20is%20the%20heroism%20of%20the%20main%20character%20with%20a%20superficial%20understanding%20of%20caste%20politics%20(as%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20Suriya%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Bhim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20or%20a%20depiction%20of%20caste-based%20poverty%20and%20helplessness.%20Even%20the%20recent%20Marathi%20film%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESatyashodhak%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20based%20on%20Mahatma%20Phule%20carefully%20shows%20oppressor%20caste%20characters%20as%20bad%20apples%20rather%20than%20being%20critical%20of%20the%20dominant%20Brahmanical%20system%20which%20denies%20basic%20human%20rights%20to%20a%20large%20section%20of%20people.%20And%20there%E2%80%99s%20the%20perpetuation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98white%20saviour%20complex%E2%80%99%20in%20Bollywood%20movies%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20an%20upper%20caste%20cop%20saves%20Dalits%20but%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20talk%20of%20dismantling%20existing%20caste%20structures%20by%20conveniently%20and%20unironically%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20caste.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20the%20exact%20reason%20we%20need%20more%20Dalit%20voices%20in%20Indian%20cinema%20to%20craft%20an%20alternate%20depiction%20of%20Bahujans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20take%20the%20examples%20of%20Mani%20Ratnam%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENaayagan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Pa.%20Ranjith%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20two%20have%20a%20striking%20similarity%20%E2%80%93%20both%20are%20set%20in%20Dharavi%20and%20are%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20vigilante%20gangster.%20What%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20that%20Kamal%E2%80%99s%20character%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENaayagan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ebelongs%20to%20the%20relatively%20well-off%20Nayakkar%20caste.%20He%20shields%20the%20Bahujan%20slum%20dwellers%20and%20rises%20up%20to%20become%20their%20saviour.%20The%20oppressor%20caste%E2%80%99s%20gaze%20and%20its%20messiah%20complex%20is%20not%20lost%20here.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Rajanikanth%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20holds%20his%20meetings%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Buddha%20Vihar.%20He%20is%20an%20anti-hero%20who%20is%20relatable%20on%20all%20fronts%20to%20those%20around%20him.%20Both%20movies%20have%20an%20interesting%20choice%20of%20colours%20as%20well%20%E2%80%93%20Kamal%20wears%20white%20when%20he%20rises%20to%20the%20top%2C%20while%20in%20Kaala%20the%20protagonist%20wears%20black%2C%20which%20is%20a%20searing%20commentary%20on%20the%20all-white%20Brahminesque%20clothing.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20critique%20of%20either%20films%2C%20but%20just%20an%20observation%20on%20how%20caste%20narratives%20are%20illustrated%20from%20the%20filmmaker%E2%80%99s%20outlook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07092709%2FScreenshot-2024-03-07-at-9.27.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x487.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07092709%2FScreenshot-2024-03-07-at-9.27.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x487.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07092709%2FScreenshot-2024-03-07-at-9.27.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x143.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07092709%2FScreenshot-2024-03-07-at-9.27.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700522%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20Kaala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20parallel%20cinema%20movement%20of%20the%2070s%20and%2080s%20which%20was%20critical%20in%20giving%20voice%20to%20marginalised%20narratives%20has%20now%20been%20wiped%20out%20by%20tentpole%20blockbusters%20and%20mid-scale%20movies%20offering%20escapism%2C%20continuing%20to%20perpetuate%20dominant%20narratives.%20This%20creates%20a%20skewed%20lens%20where%20the%20same-ness%20of%20it%20all%20overlooks%20the%20lived%20experiences%20and%20challenges%20faced%20by%20many.%20So%20yes%2C%20while%20there%20have%20been%20progressive%20and%20sometimes%2C%20LGBTQ-themed%2C%20films%20in%20the%20mainstream%2C%20ask%20yourself%20what%20the%20surname%20of%20the%20characters%20in%20those%20films%20were.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepresentation%20of%20caste%20in%20mainstream%20films%20suffers%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20attention.%20It%20is%20merely%20a%20collection%20of%20what%20filmmakers%20think%20we%20do%2C%20what%20they%20think%20we%20eat%20or%20how%20we%20dress.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20presented%2C%20many%20times%2C%20without%20research%20or%20involvement%20of%20a%20Dalit-Bahujan-Adivasi%20person%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20Namdev%20Dhasal%20to%20Sheetal%20Sathe%20to%20The%20Casteless%20Collective%2C%20Dalit%20artistes%20have%20always%20used%20performing%20arts%20in%20their%20protests%2C%20stories%2C%20folk%20tales%20and%20assertion.%20So%20it%20is%20rather%20worrying%20to%20see%20why%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20DBA%20actress%20to%20portray%20a%20person%20from%20a%20marginalised%20caste%20in%20the%20series%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMade%20in%20Heaven%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20even%20the%20Buddhist%20marriage%20sequence%20in%20it%20comes%20from%20an%20inauthentic%20point%20%E2%80%93%20thanks%20to%20the%20sheer%20Bali-fication%20and%20exoticisation%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20even%20a%20skilled%20filmmaker%20like%20Jabbar%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20films%20have%20shown%20the%20oppressed%20class%2C%20but%20even%20those%20roles%20were%20played%20by%20the%20actors%20from%20the%20oppressor%20caste.%20Cinema%20should%20be%20social%20commentary%2C%20it%20must%20critique%20power%20structures%2C%20question%20cultural%20norms%2C%20and%20hold%20a%20mirror%20to%20the%20darkest%20corners%20of%20our%20collective%20conscience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%2C%20it%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20India%20is%20home%20to%20many%20languages%20and%20dialects.%20But%20as%20we%20are%20growing%20closer%2C%20we%20are%20losing%20touch%20with%20our%20dialects.%20A%20dialect%20or%20vocabulary%20is%20a%20gateway%20into%20a%20community%E2%80%99s%20distinct%20culture.%20Each%20lost%20language%20carries%20a%20universe%20of%20stories%2C%20emotions%2C%20and%20perspectives.%20Cinema%2C%20with%20its%20powerful%20reach%2C%20can%20bridge%20that%20gap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20for%20years%2C%20I%20know%20that%20traditional%20Punjabi-Sindhi%20families%20have%20a%20grip%20over%20Bollywood%20while%20the%20Telugu%20film%20industry%20is%20ruled%20by%20the%20dominant%20Kapu-Kamma%20castes.%20This%20caste%20based%20hegemony%20is%20what%20is%20churning%20out%20template%20products%20for%20the%20celluloid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20mean%2C%20when%20was%20the%20last%20time%20you%20saw%20an%20assertive%2C%20white-collar%20Dalit%20character%20in%20a%20mainstream%20Bollywood%20romance%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20force%20fit%20it%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20we%20need%20is%20a%20subversion%20of%20stereotypical%20portrayals%20and%20reimagining%20the%20perspectives%20on%20the%20experiences%20of%20marginalised%20groups.%20Today%2C%20Indian%20films%20have%20also%20become%20a%20propaganda%20tool.%20But%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20the%20power%20of%20cinema.%20The%20lens%20of%20the%20filmmaker%20acts%20as%20a%20magnifying%20glass%2C%20and%20it%20should%20focus%20on%20societal%20anxieties%2C%20hopes%2C%20and%20unspoken%20desires%2C%20offering%20catharsis%20and%20sparking%20critical%20introspection.%20Cinema%20is%20a%20conversation%20starter%2C%20a%20bridge%20between%20cultures%2C%20and%20a%20platform%20for%20marginalised%20voices.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20time%20mainstream%20Indian%20cinema%20reflects%20the%20complexities%20of%20society%2C%20prompting%20empathy%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20progress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Vaibhav%20Wankhede%20is%20a%20writer%20who%20works%20in%20creative%20marketing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709951456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07092131%2FScreenshot-2024-03-07-at-9.19.50.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-dalit-person-in-mainstream-indian-cinema%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Upper%20caste%20saviour%20complex%20rules%20what%20scant%20representation%20of%20Dalit%20people%20there%20is%20in%20blockbusters%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-dalit-person-in-mainstream-indian-cinema%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20returns%20to%20company's%20board%20after%20probe%20clears%20him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709950339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F09%2Ffull%2F1709950263-9054.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fopenai-s-sam-altman-returns-to-company-s-board-after-probe-clears-him-124030900047_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Altman%20is%20rejoining%20the%20company's%20board%20following%20the%20findings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fopenai-s-sam-altman-returns-to-company-s-board-after-probe-clears-him-124030900047_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fopenai-s-sam-altman-returns-to-company-s-board-after-probe-clears-him-124030900047_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fopenai-s-sam-altman-returns-to-company-s-board-after-probe-clears-him-124030900047_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Better%20Sleep%20Is%20a%20Protective%20Factor%20Against%26nbsp%3BDementia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08154912%2Fmatheus-vinicius-kHHwYNA1lnM-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDementia%20is%20a%20progressive%20loss%20of%20cognitive%20abilities%2C%20such%20as%20memory%2C%20that%20is%20significant%20enough%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20daily%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20number%20of%20different%20diseases%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falzheimer.ca%2Fen%2Fabout-dementia%2Fwhat-alzheimers-disease%5C%22%3EAlzheimer%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20common%20form.%20Dementia%20is%20caused%20by%20a%20loss%20of%20neurons%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time.%20Since%2C%20by%20the%20time%20symptoms%20appear%2C%20many%20changes%20in%20the%20brain%20have%20already%20occurred%2C%20many%20scientists%20are%20focusing%20on%20studying%20the%20risk%20and%20protective%20factors%20for%20dementia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20risk%20factor%2C%20or%20conversely%2C%20a%20protective%20factor%2C%20is%20a%20condition%20or%20behaviour%20that%20increases%20or%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20developing%20a%20disease%2C%20but%20does%20not%20guarantee%20either%20outcome.%20Some%20risk%20factors%20for%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20disease%20and%20dementia%2C%20such%20as%20age%20or%20genetics%2C%20are%20not%20modifiable%2C%20but%20there%20are%20several%20other%20factors%20we%20can%20influence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Farticle%2FS0140-6736(20)30367-6%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Especifically%20lifestyle%20habits%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20our%20overall%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20risk%20factors%20include%20depression%2C%20lack%20of%20physical%20activity%2C%20social%20isolation%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20obesity%2C%20diabetes%2C%20excessive%20alcohol%20consumption%20and%20smoking%2C%20as%20well%20as%20poor%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20been%20focusing%20our%20research%20on%20the%20question%20of%20sleep%20for%20over%2010%20years%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhlbi.nih.gov%2Fscience%2Fframingham-heart-study-fhs%5C%22%3EFramingham%20Heart%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20large%20community-based%20cohort%20study%2C%20ongoing%20since%20the%201940s%2C%20the%20health%20of%20surviving%20participants%20has%20been%20monitored%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20As%20researchers%20in%20sleep%20medicine%20and%20epidemiology%2C%20we%20have%20expertise%20in%20researching%20the%20role%20of%20sleep%20and%20sleep%20disorders%20in%20cognitive%20and%20psychiatric%20brain%20ageing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20our%20research%2C%20we%20monitored%20and%20analysed%20the%20sleep%20of%20people%20aged%2060%20and%20over%20to%20see%20who%20did%20%E2%80%94%20or%20did%20not%20%E2%80%94%20develop%20dementia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleep%20as%20a%20risk%20or%20protective%20factor%20against%20dementia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESleep%20appears%20to%20play%20an%20essential%20role%20in%20a%20number%20of%20brain%20functions%2C%20such%20as%20memory.%20Good%20quality%20sleep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamaneurology%2Ffullarticle%2F2793873%5C%22%3Ecould%20therefore%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20preventing%20dementia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESleep%20is%20important%20for%20maintaining%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.1241224%5C%22%3Egood%20connections%20in%20the%20brain%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recently%2C%20research%20has%20revealed%20that%20sleep%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20function%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20a%20garbage%20truck%20for%20the%20brain%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.mad.2023.111899%5C%22%3Edeep%20sleep%20could%20be%20crucial%20for%20eliminating%20metabolic%20waste%20from%20the%20brain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20clearing%20certain%20proteins%2C%20such%20as%20those%20known%20to%20accumulate%20in%20the%20brains%20of%20people%20with%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20links%20between%20deep%20sleep%20and%20dementia%20still%20have%20to%20be%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20deep%20sleep%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20night%E2%80%99s%20sleep%2C%20we%20go%20through%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fceams-carsm.ca%2Fen%2Fa-propos-du-sommeil%2F%5C%22%3Esleep%20stages%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20succeed%20one%20another%20and%20are%20repeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENREM%20sleep%20(non-rapid%20eye%20movement%20sleep)%20is%20divided%20into%20light%20NREM%20sleep%20(NREM1%20stage)%2C%20NREM%20sleep%20(NREM2%20stage)%20and%20deep%20NREM%20sleep%2C%20also%20called%20slow-wave%20sleep%20(NREM3%20stage).%20The%20latter%20is%20associated%20with%20several%20restorative%20functions.%20Next%2C%20REM%20sleep%20(rapid%20eye%20movement%20sleep)%20is%20the%20stage%20generally%20associated%20with%20the%20most%20vivid%20dreams.%20An%20adult%20generally%20spends%20around%2015%20to%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20each%20night%20in%20deep%20sleep%2C%20if%20we%20add%20up%20all%20the%20periods%20of%20NREM3%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20sleep%20changes%20are%20common%20in%20adults%2C%20such%20as%20going%20to%20bed%20and%20waking%20up%20earlier%2C%20sleeping%20for%20shorter%20periods%20of%20time%20and%20less%20deeply%2C%20and%20waking%20up%20more%20frequently%20during%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%