%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-2-1709562016.jpeg%20625w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-2-1709562016-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-2-1709562016-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-2-1709562016-150x187.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343890%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEurasian%20kestrel%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECurrent%20Work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20earlier%2C%20his%20journey%20led%20him%20to%20work%20as%20a%20naturalist%2C%20guiding%20wildlife%20groups%20for%20Drenmo%20Lodge%20in%20Drass.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lodge%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bears.%20The%20season%20for%20these%20bears%20runs%20from%20April%20to%20October%20with%20a%20hibernation%20period%20afterwards%2C%20making%20the%20job%20seasonal.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20spotting%20season%20takes%20over%20from%20December%20to%20April%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-4-1709562414.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eurasian%20eagle%20owl%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-4-1709562414.jpeg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-4-1709562414-238x300.jpeg%20238w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-4-1709562414-500x629.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-4-1